trans-unit.source: BGE Balkan is a regional StarCraft II circuit that takes place every week. Players from the Balkan region compete in a series of matches to earn points and prizes.

The circuit is open to all players from the Balkan region, and it's free to participate. The top players from each week will earn points that will count towards guaranteed â‚¬150 prize pool at the end of the month.
50% of all donations during game days are added on top of the guaranteed prize pool for the month. You can donate through:
Matches are played on the EU server, and players are required to join the BGE Balkan Discord to communicate with the admins and other players. See the full Rulebook for more information.

Bellum Gens Elite is a premier esports LAN event organized in Bulgaria. Ancient history and traditions, and beautiful scenery combine with high-level action-packed esports competition to bring you an unforgettable experience.

The Summer Theater in Stara Zagora is located at the foot of largest city park in Bulgaria. This open-air masterpiece combines nature and ancient traditions with modern architecture into a unique experience for the audience.

The city hosting this event has more than 8000 years of history! Ancient forums, Roman murals and mosaics, 2000-year-old theaters, bath houses, and aqueducts, it's all beneath your feet and everywhere around you. Traditions and modern esports come together at this unique place!

Bellum Gens Elite Balkan weekly online circuit launches in November 2024 and presents every player in the Balkan region with the opportunity to participate in weekly online matches to earn points towards cash prizes.
Open to everyone in the Balkan region
Compete weekly to earn points towards monthly cash prizes
Bellum Gens joined forces with the Bulgarian StarCraft League and Stara Zagora Municipality to deliver an epic esports experience!
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora 2020 brought the top Counter-Strike talent in the region to compete under one roof for a prize pool of $10,000!
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora was one of the few LAN events held in 2020 and due to Covid-19 lockdowns and travel restrictions, only 10 teams were able to participate in the LAN finals.

Registrations are restricted to participants from the Balkan countries. Registrations have no age restrictions. Registrations for this event are not in any way binding and participation can be halted by the registrant at any point of time. Registrations can also be deleted by the user through the user profile settings menu.

Registrations show intent for participation, but weekly participation would require timely weekly check-ins and being on-time for the matches. All applicants must reside in one of the listed Balkan countries. If an applicant is discovered to permanently reside outside of the listed Balkan countries, that would lead to permanent disqualification from the league and nullification of any points earned.
Provided battle tag, discord ID, should match with the accounts the applicant uses during the League.
Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora 2025 will take place June 4-7th! Clement "Clem" Desplanches returns to defend his 2024 title against all the top contenders!
Esports Business League is a gaming event for your office! Build better team bonds by friendly or competitive gaming, or get your team to compete against other companies to show how good you are!

Recruit your team and manage your team member roles, team strategies, practice times and more. The only online Counter-Strike strategy editor freely available to everyone! Discuss public strategies with everyone and build private strategies for your team.

Bellum Gens is a gaming and esports event organizer and consultant focused on the development and popularization of esports in Bulgaria. We want to make esports a recognizable topic for the business and thus to help the development of all esports project in Bulgaria and on the Balkans. If you take interest in esports and want to advertise through esports, position your brand in tournaments, streams, or other gaming and esports channels, then we can help! Contact us for more information on available opportunities.

Bellum Gens is the organizer of the premier Bellum Gen Elite esports event. First held in the town of Stara Zagora, under the name Bellum Gens Elite - Stara Zagora, BGE brought the top Counter-Strike talent in the region to compete under one roof for a prize pool of $10,000! Bellum Gens Elite Stara Zagora 2024 features top StarCraft II players from around the world with a prize pool of â‚¬10000!

Bellum Gens is the organizer of the Esports Business League - a competitive amateur gaming event for the office. Miltiple companies in Bulgaria participated in seasons one and two of the Esports Business League both for fun and team building and to show which company has the best gamers among their employees!

Bellum Gens offers a Counter-Strike team finding and team management application, which allows players to look for teams matching their skill and availability, and team owners to manage their teams' roster and general organization. Because Counter-Strike is a team game!
